data.description: Welcome home! This stunning one of a kind property in Raindance that was built 2 years ago, vaulted ceilings, featuring lots of windows bringing in light,  4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. Park your vehicles with ease in the attached 2-car garage, equipped with a convenient Bluetooth opener for effortless access.Step inside to discover luxurious touches throughout, including beautiful LVP flooring and a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings Situated on a generous corner lot, this home offers privacy and curb appeal. Enjoy outdoor gatherings in the fully fenced yard, complete with a covered patio and deck for al fresco dining and relaxation.Venture downstairs to find a fully finished basement, offering even more living space to customize to your needs. The yard is meticulously landscaped with additional flatwork and sprinkler system, creating a picturesque backdrop for outdoor enjoyment. As a bonus, the seller is offering a $5,000 concession!!  Preferred Lender is also offering lender-paid temporary buy-down (restrictions apply). Additionally, enjoy peace of mind with a First American Home Warranty included. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property - schedule your showing today and start envisioning the possibilities!
